1. *Dame* su mnoge stvari naučile o životu. (The ladies have learned many things about life.)

2. On je svojim *damama* poklonio cveće. (He gave flowers to his ladies.)

3. Ona je veče provedla sa svojim *damama*. (She spent the evening with her ladies.)

4. U modernom svetu, *dama* se ne mora udati za ljubav. (In the modern world, a lady does not have to marry for love.)

5. *Dame* često nosili raskošne haljine. (The ladies often wore luxurious dresses.)

6. Ona je bila *dama* u punom smislu te reči. (She was a lady in the full sense of the word.)